OL,6,FCCTV footage released by Northumbria
OL,7,FPolice shows Weatherald stealing the
OL,8,Fbottles of alcohol
OL,10,FA burglar was caught on CCTV swiping
OL,11,Ften bottles of alcohol from a city
OL,12,Fcentre bar.
OL,14,FJohn Weatherald forced his way into
OL,15,FBobby's Bar, on Low Row, Sunderland,
OL,16,Fand stole bottles of Tequila Rose,
OL,17,FSmirnoff and Captain Morgan from the
OL,18,Ffridges before making off.
