OL,3,CCCTV captures burglar raiding rum,
OL,4,Cvodka and tequila from bar's fridges
OL,6,FThe 54-year-old was caught in the act
OL,7,Fon CCTV on the evening of 8 April, and
OL,8,Fidentified by officers. He was
OL,9,Farrested and charged with burglary the
OL,10,Ffollowing day.
OL,12,FWeatherald, of St Barnabas Way,
OL,13,FSunderland, appeared before
OL,14,Fmagistrates on South Tyneside on 10
OL,15,FApril where he admitted the offence
OL,16,Fand was jailed for 22 weeks.
