OL,6,FNorthumbria Police Sergeant Dave
OL,7,FCatton said: "This was a case of
OL,8,Ffantastic teamwork between teams of
OL,9,Fofficers, especially the Millfield
OL,10,FNeighbourhood Team, as well as our
OL,11,Fcriminal justice partners to reach a
OL,12,Fswift and successful outcome."
OL,14,FHe continued: "Weatherald showed a
OL,15,Ftotal disregard for the law and others
OL,16,Fas he broke into the bar and swiped
OL,17,Fvarious bottles of alcohol ` in the
OL,18,Fhope that he would not be caught.
