OL,6,F"We all want to live, work and visit a
OL,7,Fcity centre that is hassle-free and
OL,8,Fsafe for all. Burglary is such an
OL,9,Fintrusive crime and we make no apology
OL,10,Ffor taking strong and robust action
OL,11,Fagainst offenders."
OL,13,FWeatherald was identified in the
OL,14,Ffootage by officers from the
OL,15,FSunderland Altogether Improving Lives
OL,16,F(SAIL) partnership.
